node.title: 'It's really challenging': Waiting 10 hours for the first cuddle
node.description: Tide and Kove were born prematurely at 34 weeks and are still at the hospital's specialist nursery. Their parents hope the whole family will be home by Christmas.

node.title: Four children die in house fire in Melbourne's south-west
node.description: Arson squad detectives are investigating the cause of the blaze in Werribee, which left three people in hospital and four children dead.

node.title: Father's missing war medal finds its way back to his daughters
node.description: A "bizarre" chain of events leads to three sisters being reunited with their father's Korean War medal, more than half a century after he left his family, never to return.
